column4: [31391.045186] Buffer I/O error on device sr0, logical block 1 what does this mean?? plz?
i saw is as the result of dmesg | tail, while trying to resolve why my 4in1 card reader wasn't working
the system is a new install it can't be hd? right?
/dev/sr0 is CD-ROM, not hard-drive. Hard drives are /dev/sdXN
